{"tid":2406884,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣蘋果日報：BMW衝入店家起火釀5死　女子衝火場救未婚夫全身8成燒傷","createTime":"2021-02-13T14:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T00:16:14.000Z","uid":290404,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"df15da361946e0475dce915eae6466c0d064c8e7","tid":2406884,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210213/4S6ZFJWDYVABNNVPN4JQ7CG4U4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210213%2F4S6ZFJWDYVABNNVPN4JQ7CG4U4%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=05daed60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210213%2F4S6ZFJWDYVABNNVPN4JQ7CG4U4%2F&h=45a39b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210213/4S6ZFJWDYVABNNVPN4JQ7CG4U4/</a><br />\n<br />\n大年初二，新加坡發生一起重大車禍，一輛BMW轎車疑因超速失控，撞入路邊店家後爆炸起火，車上5人當場燒死，另一名女子為了要救未婚夫衝進火場，結果全身八成面積燒傷，目前仍在醫院急救中。<br />\n<br />\n《星洲日報》報導，這起意外發生在當地時間周六(13日)清晨約5時40分，一輛由一名29歲男子駕駛的BMW轎車，行經丹絨巴葛路時疑因車速過快，失控撞進路邊一家商店，車輛立刻起火燃燒，警方獲報到場時車上5人已全數燒死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/vRYuv_xME5zHlp5hS-lwymsja8w=/1118x749/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HEHWMPIIOJGW7LYABO3OPGXNUQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvRYuv_xME5zHlp5hS-lwymsja8w%3D%2F1118x749%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHEHWMPIIOJGW7LYABO3OPGXNUQ.JPG&h=790758b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66d94692587452111e58e05ff456d230ba4669e2","tid":2406884,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"fe924df9d29e12c48a19117a9c30f75eb0b4d24d","tid":2406884,"uid":44826,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:40:06.000Z